Description: Naruto and his allies face off against a horde of ninja soldiers, some of whom are back from the dead and former friends.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 56
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Sailor Moon fights for justice in the name of the Moon and the mysterious Moon Princess. Along the way, she recruits other girls to be Sailor Scouts and join her fight against evil.
Title: SAILOR MOON, VOL. 5
Author: Naoko Takeuchi

Description: Secret crushes and blackmail. It sounds like this popular manga series, reprinted for the first time in the United States, has perfectly captured high school.
Title: FLOWERS OF EVIL, VOL. 1
Author: Shuzo Oshimi

Description: Mafuyu, who has been sent to a rural school to change her delinquent ways, has two tasks over the summer: catch up on homework and sing the praises of her teacher to one of his colleagues.
Title: ORESAMA TEACHER, VOL. 8
Author: Izumi Tsubaki

Description: The Pokemon saga continues with the introduction of two new trainers: Black and White.
Title: POKEMON BLACK AND WHITE, VOL. 7
Author: Hidenori Kusaka

Description: Welcome to life in Ikebukuro, a Japanese city with lots of unusual activity, including the Black Biker, who is rumored to be headless.
Title: DURARARA!!, VOL. 2
Author: Ryohgo Narita

Description: Monkey D. Luffy and his motley crew of would-be pirates search for a legendary treasure called “One Piece.” In this volume, the crew set sail for Fish-man Island at the bottom of the sea.
Title: ONE PIECE, VOL. 62
Author: Eiichiro Oda

Description: Sebastian is a loyal butler who moves easily from dinner parties to the underworld. Is he too good to be true? Is he even human?
Title: BLACK BUTLER, VOL. 9
Author: Yana Toboso

Description: Life in a high school filled with werewolves and vampires continues.
Title: ROSARIO+VAMPIRE, SEASON II, VOL. 8
Author: Akihisa Ikeda

Description: Mizuki is the the lead guitarist in an all-girl rock band. Akira is from an all-boy school and wants to join. In this volume, Akira's middle school tutor has returned and threatens to reveal a secret from his past.
Title: AI ORE: LOVE ME, VOL. 5
Author: Mayu Shinjo
